import org.apache.spark.MLlib.regression.+

val data = rawData.map{line =>
    val values = line.split(',').map(_.toDouble)
    val featureVector = Vectors.dense(values.init)
    val label = values.last-1
    LabeledPoint(label, featureVector)
}
